{"tid":2163511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」Trump赦免Susan B. Anthony","createTime":"2020-08-18T17:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T17:30:18.000Z","uid":313615,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4575fb78a5979bcb3a17ca7d5843e74655ca2a72","tid":2163511,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:01:22.000Z","msg":"Trump says he will pardon Susan B. Anthony. Anthony was arrested for voting in 1872 in violation of laws permitting only men to vote.<br />\n<br />\n佢將赦免婦女選舉權領導人蘇珊&middot;安東尼「Susan B. Anthony」，後者1872年因非法投票而被定罪。正係該法案賦予咗美國女性選舉權。"},{"pid":"6a624d805a7e715181388b3ba058d306364b3d99","tid":2163511,"uid":137160,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:04:29.000Z","msg":"撚狗到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67b181ac6f785a59f02db9cf71b0679e3b491be","tid":2163511,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed0b2a59c40e0161c124650e93f75532b9ad4b94","tid":2163511,"uid":337826,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:04:57.000Z","msg":"左膠一定會話侵只係為選票而做而非真心<br />\n所以十一月一定要投拜登"},{"pid":"1a5e0631293c954bdf08cb63b690c6c28adf3b46","tid":2163511,"uid":352851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"in trump we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55ac5b62cf271870f12ac0eea598283e7dda234","tid":2163511,"uid":62948,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"我有冇睇錯？1872年？"},{"pid":"3cfd775b5c52ff9b986f10a66a9bb818c3302a11","tid":2163511,"uid":331739,"like":